      "text": [
        " سَفَرٍ فَقَالَ «لَوْ صَلَحَتِ اَلنَّافِلَةُ فِي اَلسَّفَرِ تَمَّتِ اَلْفَرِيضَةُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1292 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about performing the supererogatory (nafilah) prayers during the day while traveling.\nImam (as) said: \"If it were appropriate to perform the nafilah (supererogatory) prayers during travel, then the obligatory (fardh) prayers would have been completed (in full)”."
        ]
      }
    },
